Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 果然漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已經準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一起喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像今天這樣一起喝也是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天天氣似乎會很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 感謝你一直以來的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能這樣迎來明天全都多虧了姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦 你這樣我會忍不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出嫁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 也就是那樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然發生了不少事 但沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的話一定會讓你幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是每天早上都在堅持啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.27,0:03:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這是朝倉君的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡懶覺 可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是像以前那樣去叫你起床比較好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用啦 我一個人沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是準備了美妙的叫醒方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙的叫醒方式是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘 密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是麻煩你真過意不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我是自己願意才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是畢竟做起來很麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了我大忙呢 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你了呢 小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直受你的關照 真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有小鳥在的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這樣可是會讓其他人眼饞的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美 美春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位在上學途中的恩恩愛愛如果不適可而止的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會被當作違反風紀而受到嚴格管束的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫恩恩愛愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 不純異性交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡像是不純異性交往啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那就是純真異性交往了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來不還是恩恩愛愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小鳥 怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟朝倉君的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有進展嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有進展什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟小鳥很晚熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上對方又是超級遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這個又沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不討厭他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再積極主動一點的話是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人獨處的時候不是挺多的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能那樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為… 朝倉君他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然也明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經過了一年了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是雞肉汆鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的汆鍋 就是為了突出肉的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不使用其它的調味料 將白菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 感覺真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}…洋蔥等材料放入後製成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉要來點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我還有便當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}不同地區的做法都有所不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然愛妻便當也不錯 但火鍋也是很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛妻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯哦 別光是吃白河學姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也吃吃美春的便當哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誇張的東西是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了朝倉學長而努力製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉麵包 香蕉飯 外加香蕉蕎麥面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香蕉的全包宴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵包加飯外帶蕎麥面 全是碳水化合物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉裡面充滿了營養 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 請用吧 朝倉學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 我就不用了 畢竟已經有小鳥的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我沒收了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說愛妻便當可是違反風紀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你先吃了美春的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是可以破例原諒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}才不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}便當還我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小美春動不動就惹朝倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻很歡樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是妹妹向哥哥撒嬌呢 還是說小狗撒歡兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之就是想被人調戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 總是總是總是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙到底是從哪兒冒出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長還很年輕 能把美春的全部吃完的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這種問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}光吃白河學姐的便當 人家不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 比起消沉來還是喧鬧的好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}你那幾個便當我更接受不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}別說這種話 先吃吃看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學精神了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}誰會吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}喂 小鳥 你也來幫幫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼白河跟朝倉 他們倆如何了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事你不要問我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得感覺不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎… 那麼他們已經成為戀人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說了別問我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 朝倉 白河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們已經成為戀人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉並 你難道不懂察言觀色…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個詞嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位還是這麼厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃 杉並！ 可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君 今天晚飯想吃什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是女朋友親自下廚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的啦 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這個黃瓜是附送的 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君 過來這邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 快來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該 該是時候回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 還是我去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 我在想茶杯哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛拿去洗過了 在那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 原來在那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的事就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是弄到這麼晚 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然保證了李徵今後的官職和權利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他自己卻覺得還不如做個詩人死後可以留名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 今天還有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 之後再聯繫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是認真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能總是這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 這是要打掃音夢前輩的房間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 朝倉君 其實也不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美春總覺得好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 美春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 最後作出決定的還是朝倉學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很煩惱的 不知道想過了多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還是這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然朝倉同學已經下定決心了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們肯定會幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音夢前輩的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是隻小狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為因為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音夢前輩的味道就像香蕉的味道一樣能讓美春沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美春總是死纏著音夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都曾一樣是風紀委員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音夢前輩對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能一起分享身心和香蕉還有朝倉學長的關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和香蕉是同一等級啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 真不想就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣說的話 永遠都沒辦法收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念啊 附屬中學時的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫得真認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個優等生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:17:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為某個人不肯認真記筆記 所以音夢才如此努力的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 音夢的辛苦都付之流水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正在考試之前你肯定要看音夢的筆記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理筆記？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連切蔬菜的姿勢都有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西我可沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為朝倉你總說是什麼殺人料理嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音夢可是相當介意的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在偷偷學習的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻沒有半點進步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個一點神經都沒有的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為這個笨哥哥著想 你還真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天色暗下來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把燈打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺小的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是音夢最喜歡的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還留著啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和我成為真正的兄妹時所穿著的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是想留作紀念而一直用心保存著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還是留下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定要全收拾掉了的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音夢走後的一年 我成了個廢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有大家一直支撐著 支撐著這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能重新振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 我在內心中還是對音夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我應該重視的是現在支撐著我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很重視我 我怎麼能不重視大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這房間不能永遠都這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是不禁會想 這真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.70,0:19:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白河同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.13,0:20:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君 真的沒感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把音夢同學的房間收拾乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.95,0:20:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣的話 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對小鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小鳥你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在等這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.84,0:22:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都想聽到的這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉君
